s://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Ud2wuThahY&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyHKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=665f2ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Ud2wuThahY</a>"},{"pid":"e6d9d84d1506f613f08292df3430ceff0de7bdf4","tid":2368204,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"早排老母成日買雞尾包畀我當早餐<br />\n之後食得太多叫佢唔好買住<br />\n依家長期唔食早餐<br />\n一起身係會肚餓但一陣個感覺就冇左<br />\n去到兩點先食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常夜晚個餐係8點-10點內<br />\n即係計返原來我每日斷食14-16小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}